去外國散播變種病毒是上上策！因為外國要繼續倚賴中国"},{"pid":"896624ed725f4417ef19f3c58fbf3228a4a35074","tid":2516703,"uid":211754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T23:45:04.000Z","msg":"支持維尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b78ba877a89e601709f697524c6d76f2d51064f","tid":2516703,"uid":237465,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T23:48:31.000Z","msg":"咁幾時親自帶兵打鳩全世界 ?  快撚D啦唔該.  唔係點揚國威 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf39f9dbd6b726492a1d9fe44385825ea1a21b8b","tid":2516703,"uid":65686,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T23:53:06.000Z","msg":"習大大出年連任多一屆，繼續鴻圖大業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d67e44b3ae72ef5752cb43edbbd98ce5099a96e","tid":2516703,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T23:53:52.000Z","msg":"大王英明"},{"pid":"1e1374866346d3d474b47072e07bcaf60e91021d","tid":2516703,"uid":266519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3d67e44b3ae72ef5752cb43edbbd98ce5099a96e","tid":2516703,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T23:53:52.000Z","msg":"大王英明"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:10:43.000Z","msg":"幾時得閒修復埋俄羅斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b447bb23dde66fd12efd864d4c022e5fdcf68e3","tid":2516703,"uid":331551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:14:52.000Z","msg":"咁有信心 ....<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26b83e88c36690a10c8e4981c7adbdec6baf6b86","tid":2516703,"uid":19527,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:17:19.000Z","msg":"更加證明武肺係中共製造<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face